recyclable paper next week,

273
00:11:57,625 --> 00:11:58,458
so get your stack ready.

274
00:11:58,541 --> 00:12:00,708
[ALL]
Get out of here!

275
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:04,083
[NEO]
It seems we're out of options.

276
00:12:04,166 --> 00:12:07,541
The question is: what to draw?

277
00:12:07,625 --> 00:12:08,541
Light bulb!

278
00:12:08,625 --> 00:12:10,666
Yes, what've you got, Doctor?

279
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:15,458
[PSYCHO] Why don't we turn
Handa... into a cute girl?

280
00:12:15,541 --> 00:12:17,333
