328
00:14:15,208 --> 00:14:17,791
[NEO] Well. Because I...
I like to feel the breeze!

329
00:14:17,875 --> 00:14:19,541
[HANDA]
Wow. They responded!

330
00:14:19,625 --> 00:14:22,875
Okay. I guess that's a reason.

331
00:14:22,958 --> 00:14:24,416
[NEO]
I'm glad he replied.

332
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:25,750
For a second there,

333
00:14:25,833 --> 00:14:27,833
I thought I was stupid
for taking this approach.

334
00:14:27,916 --> 00:14:32,500
Gotta focus. Be one with Merina!
