335
00:14:32,583 --> 00:14:36,708
[NEO] Tell me, Master.
What do you really think of me?

336
00:14:36,791 --> 00:14:38,583
[HANDA] That's a pretty
forward thing to ask someone

337
00:14:38,666 --> 00:14:43,583
