340
00:14:47,958 --> 00:14:50,291
[NEO]
Wow! You think I'm fine?

341
00:14:50,375 --> 00:14:53,541
Oh, my! You're such
a smooth operator!

342
00:14:53,625 --> 00:14:54,875
[HANDA]
All right.

343
00:14:54,958 --> 00:14:56,333
I don't know why, but they
seem happy with that.

344
00:14:56,416 --> 00:14:58,625
[NEO chuckles]
So even Handa

345
00:14:58,708 --> 00:15:01,791
is no match for Merina's
feminine charms!

346
00:15:03,541 --> 00:15:05,291
[NEO]
I guess I can give him a treat.

347
00:15:05,375 --> 00:15:08,083
[NEO] Oh, Master,
