I need for my story!

356
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,625
[NEO]
Take it off! Take it off!

357
00:15:27,708 --> 00:15:29,666
[HANDA groaning]

358
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:32,083
[NEO]
This is it!

359
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:39,375
[HANDA]
You may just be a toy,

360
00:15:39,458 --> 00:15:42,791
but you're still a lady and
should be treated like one.

361
00:15:42,875 --> 00:15:44,958
I don't need that
handkerchief back.

362
00:15:45,041 --> 00:15:49,541
Next time, play with someone
who appreciates you.

363
00:15:49,625 --> 00:15:51,416
Not me.

364
00:15:53,041 --> 00:15:55,291
[NEO]
"Someone who appreciates her?"

365
00:15:55,375 --> 00:15:58,500
Merina and I have been together
for over ten years now.

366
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:00,541
