her this way.

367
00:16:00,625 --> 00:16:02,666
Have I been taking
advantage of her?

368
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:05,708
Forgive me. I'm...
I'm so sorry, Merina!

369
00:16:05,791 --> 00:16:09,083
I never even thought twice
about taking off your skirt!

370
00:16:09,166 --> 00:16:10,333
Thank you, Handa.

371
00:16:10,416 --> 00:16:13,791
You've shown me
there's another way!

372
00:16:13,875 --> 00:16:18,541
I swear... the next comic I
draw will be worthy of you!

373
00:16:18,625 --> 00:16:20,125
[HANDA]
I know.

374
00:16:20,208 --> 00:16:25,333
