390
00:16:59,625 --> 00:17:02,541
Handa- <i>chan</i> would never
act so indecently!

391
00:17:02,625 --> 00:17:05,458
Uh! But there's no point
in making a manga

392
00:17:05,541 --> 00:17:07,083
