down and read mine?

397
00:17:16,333 --> 00:17:18,000
In here, she's a space soldier

398
00:17:18,083 --> 00:17:19,500
that fights
intergalactic battles

399
00:17:19,583 --> 00:17:21,041
for her captain boyfriend!

400
00:17:21,125 --> 00:17:21,791
[NEO grunts]

401
00:17:21,875 --> 00:17:24,291
[groaning]

402
00:17:24,375 --> 00:17:25,708
My poor face!

403
00:17:25,791 --> 00:17:28,750
