the tropes of the genre!

406
00:17:31,791 --> 00:17:33,416
Well don't!

407
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:35,333
The inner charm and natural
beauty of Handa- <i>chan</i> is all

408
00:17:35,416 --> 00:17:37,791
