419
00:18:00,333 --> 00:18:02,916
But, in this case, we
have no other choice

420
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:05,875
but to take a
different approach.

421
00:18:05,958 --> 00:18:07,791
What, do you think
the comic you wrote

422
00:18:07,875 --> 00:18:10,333
is going to make us
change our minds?

423
00:18:10,416 --> 00:18:12,041
Yes, I do.

424
00:18:12,125 --> 00:18:14,041
I spent this whole past week
getting to know Handa- <i>chan</i> ,

425
00:18:14,125 --> 00:18:16,208
and, quite frankly,
it changed me.

426
00:18:16,291 --> 00:18:17,625
After this experience,

427
00:18:17,708 --> 00:18:20,375
