437
00:18:43,041 --> 00:18:46,333
This is the heroine the world
has been looking for!

438
00:18:46,416 --> 00:18:49,458
Handa- <i>chan</i> ! I'm not
worthy of your love!

439
00:18:49,541 --> 00:18:52,250
This panel where she puts
the robe on the naked girl

440
00:18:52,333 --> 00:18:54,125
is truly inspiring!

441
00:18:54,208 --> 00:18:55,375
I know.

442
00:18:55,458 --> 00:18:56,708
The first time I saw it,

443
00:18:56,791 --> 00:18:59,375
I was so moved that I wept
openly like a child.

444
00:18:59,458 --> 00:19:01,166
We can't waste any more time!

445
00:19:01,250 --> 00:19:02,708
If we're going to
make our deadline,

446
00:19:02,791 --> 00:19:04,500
we have to get the copies
ready for print!

447
00:19:04,583 --> 00:19:05,750
You're right.

448
00:19:05,833 --> 00:19:07,875
The school festival is
