452
00:19:14,958 --> 00:19:16,083
Come on!

453
00:19:16,166 --> 00:19:18,041
[NEO]
All right! Let's go!

454
00:19:18,125 --> 00:19:21,041
[TAKOYAKI] Time to find him
and show him this masterpiece!

455
00:19:21,125 --> 00:19:23,041
Handa!

456
00:19:23,125 --> 00:19:25,541
[NEO] Woo! My chance to
speak to Handa face-to-face

457
00:19:25,625 --> 00:19:27,125
