460
00:19:38,833 --> 00:19:43,208
'Scuse me guys. I'm here
to get the recycling boxes.

461
00:19:43,291 --> 00:19:47,625
Huh? Guess this is it. Comics?

462
00:19:47,708 --> 00:19:48,958
Where is he?

463
00:19:49,041 --> 00:19:51,666
I don't know, but we
really need to find him.

464
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:55,125
Oh, hey. It's the Cute Girls
something something club.

465
00:19:55,208 --> 00:19:58,041
<i>Bishoujo</i> . Anyway, you know
if Handa's still here?

466
00:19:58,125 --> 00:20:00,958
Yes, he's currently helping us
collect the recyclable paper

467
00:20:01,041 --> 00:20:02,625
