I'm so tired!

490
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:56,625
Oh, no! Too late.

491
00:20:59,875 --> 00:21:01,416
[NEO]
Handa?

492
00:21:02,250 --> 00:21:04,791
But why is he
chasing the truck?

493
00:21:04,875 --> 00:21:08,375
[HANDA] I'm the one
who threw them away!

494
00:21:08,458 --> 00:21:09,166
[ALL gasping]

495
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:10,333
He's so fast.

496
00:21:10,416 --> 00:21:12,750
Save Handa- <i>chan</i> !

497
00:21:17,916 --> 00:21:21,666
[TAKOYAKI]
Whoa! The truck's coming back!

498
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:24,916
Handa did all that to protect
our <i>waifu</i> from harm!

499
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,041
Yatta!

500
00:21:26,125 --> 00:21:28,375
Yeah! Guys! This is
the best day ever!

501
00:21:28,458 --> 00:21:30,000
You were right all along, Chief,

502
00:21:30,083 --> 00:21:32,416
Handa is as pure and as kind
as Handa- <i>chan</i> herself,

503
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:34,166
even if he isn't as cute!

504
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:37,625
[PSYCHO laughs] Let's make
sure they're undamaged!

505
00:21:37,708 --> 00:21:42,916
Handa! Truly. Thank you.

506
00:21:43,583 --> 00:21:45,333
[HANDA]
That was tough, but worth it.

507
00:21:45,416 --> 00:21:46,833
I bet they were itching
to tell everyone

508
00:21:46,916 --> 00:21:48,875
I threw away their
stuff on purpose.

509
00:21:48,958 --> 00:21:50,416
[NEO]
Well? Have you found them yet?

510
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,833
[TAKOYAKI] Where are they?
Oh, wait, oh! Is this...?

511
00:21:52,916 --> 00:21:55,708
Man, that sure was a close
one, wasn't it, Handa?

512
00:21:55,791 --> 00:21:57,958
Wow, I wonder what
idiot threw them away.

513
00:21:58,041 --> 00:21:59,958
[HANDA]
You trying to start something?

514
00:22:00,041 --> 00:22:01,541
[TAKOYAKI]
Oh. They gotta be here.

515
00:22:01,625 --> 00:22:03,458
[ALL gasping]

516
00:22:04,958 --> 00:22:06,833
[HANDA grunts]

517
00:22:10,041 --> 00:22:12,333
[HANDA-CHAN moans]

518
00:22:13,291 --> 00:22:15,333
[HANDA gasping]

519
00:22:15,416 --> 00:22:18,750
[NEO]
Yay! We found them at last!

520
00:22:18,833 --> 00:22:20,541
[HANDA]
What the...?

521
00:23:51,666 --> 00:23:53,833
[TAKOYAKI] We've still got a bit
before the school festival,

522
00:23:53,916 --> 00:23:55,583
but our presales
are stacking up!

523
00:23:55,666 --> 00:23:57,333
You know, none of this
would be happening

524
00:23:57,416 --> 00:23:59,500
if Handa hadn't protected
our comics for us.

525
00:23:59,583 --> 00:24:01,333
That's true.

526
00:24:01,416 --> 00:24:02,541
What are you sketching now?

527
00:24:02,625 --> 00:24:04,708
Is it a new cutie?

528
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:12,500
It's not what it looks like!

529
00:24:12,583 --> 00:24:14,583
I'm just improving
my talents, okay?

530
00:24:14,666 --> 00:24:15,708
[bell rings]

531
00:24:15,791 --> 00:24:16,958
[KAWAFUJI]
That's all it took

532
00:24:17,041 --> 00:24:19,916
for the chief to wander
down the forbidden path.

